text: Tatiana Golovin (born 25 January 1988 in Moscow, Russia) is a professional female tennis player. She moved to Paris, France and earned French citizenship. She won the 2004 French Open mixed-doubles event with Richard Gasquet. She lives in Miami, Florida. She speaks English and French. ==WTA Tour titles== ===Singles=== *2007 Amelia Island defeated Nadia Petrova ===Singles finalist=== *2004 Birmingham lost to Maria Sharapova *2005 Tokyo lost to Nicole Vaidišová *2006 Stuttgart lost to Nadia Petrova ==Grand Slam titles== ===Mixed doubles=== *2004 French Open with Richard Gasquet defeated Cara Black and Wayne Black == Other websites == * * Category:1988 births Category:Living people Category:Russian tennis players
